_sText:
My first map. It is my build of the famous map gg_fy_iceworld. This is mostly for practice but i figured I would put it up anyways. 

Just drop the file into your cstrike\maps folder in steam and it will show up on the map listings. No custom textures or anything fancy.

A special thanks to the original creators of gg_fy_iceworld.

Enjoy!
